 Roads to avoid

 Special traffic restrictions have been imposed on the following roads for Kali puja:

 ankim Chatterjee Street, Shyama Charan Dey Street, Tollygunge Road, SN Banerjee Road, Rashbehari Avenue, Balaram Bose Ghat Road, Raja Ram Mohan Roy Sarani, Keshub Chandra Sen Street and Northern Channel of Southern Avenue will be closed from 4 pm to 4 am.

 alighat Road, Sadananda Road and Hazra Road will also remain closed.

